{
    "title": "Senhora Tentação",
    "artist": "Cartola",
    "composer": "Silas De Oliveira / Joaquim Ilarindo",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7/G\">C7/G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7(5-)\">F#m7(5-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sinto abalada minha calma</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Embriagada minh'alma</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Efeito da sua sedução</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Óh,            minha romântica senhora tentação</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7/G\">C7/G</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7(5-)\">F#m7(5-)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não deixe que eu venha sucumbir</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Neste vendaval de paixão</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Óh,            minha romântica senhora tentação</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7/G\">C7/G</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7(5-)\">F#m7(5-)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não deixe que eu venha sucumbir</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ebm7\">Ebm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Neste vendaval de paixão</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ebm7\">Ebm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Jamais pensei em minha vida</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sentir tamanha emoção</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7(5-)\">F#m7(5-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Será que o amor por ironia</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em/D\">Em/D</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7(5-)/C\">F#m7(5-)/C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Deu-me esta fantasia</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vestida de obsessão?</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am/G\">Am/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  A ti confesso que me apaixonei</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#º\">F#º</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Será uma maldição? Não sei</span>\n",
